author: Michael Wayland
title: Worst yet to come as coronavirus takes its toll on auto sales
description: The coronavirus, led by stay-at-home regulations, brought U.S. vehicle sales to a grinding halt in many areas of the country and the worst is still yet to come, according to industry officials.
content:
A luxury sports car sits on display in a dealership in Manhattan on November 30, 2017 in New York City.
